ownedComment.body:
It is not possible for an instance 'x' of Book to be related twice to the same instance 'y' of author. The same as ORM internal Uniqueness Constraint.
The following OCL constraints are necessary in OntoUML
context _'Book' inv : self.authorship->isUnique(author) context _'Author' inv : self.authorship->isUnique(book)
